hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
6594,"ham ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan sunaya aur aap sachchon ke sachey they aur aap ki sachchai ki zabardast gawahi di gaee. farmaya ke tum mein se har shakhs pahley apni maa ke pet mein chalis (40) din tak nutfaa hi rakha jata hai. phir itni hi muddat main ( علقة ( yani khoon ki phutkii banta hai phir itney hi arse main ( مضغة ( (yani gosht ka lothdaa ( phir char maah baad Allah Taala aik farishta bhejta hai aur uske barey mein) maa ke pet hi mein) char baton ke likhney ka hukm diya jata hai. uski rozii ka, uski maut ka, iska ke wo bad-bakht hai ya nek bakht. to Allah ki qasam, tum mein se aik shakhs dozakh walon ke se kaam karta rehta hai aur jab uske aur dozakh ke darmyan sirf aik baalisht ka fasla ya aik hath ka fasla baqi reh jata hai to uski taqdeer is par ghalib aati hai aur wo jannat walon ke se kaam karne lagta hai aur jannat mein jata hai. isi tarah aik shakhs jannat walon ke se kaam karta rehta hai aur jab uske aur jannat ke darmyan aik hath ka fasla baqi reh jata hai to uski taqdeer is par ghalib aati hai aur wo dozakh walon ke kaam karne lagta hai aur dozakh mein jata hai. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) kehtey hain ke Aadam-bin-abii-Ayaas ne apni riwayat mein yun kaha ke jab aik hath ka fasla reh jata hai."
6595,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne maa k pet par aik farishta muqarrar kar diya hai aur wo kehta rehta hai ke aey rab! ye ( نطفة ( qarar paya hai. aey rab! ab ( علقة ( yani jama hua khoon bin gaya hai. aey rab! ab ( مضغة‏ . Mina ( ) gosht ka lothdaa (bin gaya hai. phir jab Allah Taala chahta hai ke uski paidaaish poori karey to wo poochhta hai aey rab ladka hai ya ladki ? nek hai ya bura ? uski rozii kya hogi ? uski maut Kab hogi ? isi tarah ye sab baatein maa ke pet hi mein likh di jati hain, duniya mein usi ke mutabiq zahir hota hai."
6596,aik sahib ne (yani khud unhon-ne) arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya jannat ke log jahannamiyon mein se pahchaaney ja chukey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''haan'' unhon-ne kaha ke phir amal karne waley kyon amal karein? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har shakhs wahi amal karta hai jiske liye wo paida kya gaya hai ya jiske liye usey sahoolat di gaee hai.
6597,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ki aulad ke barey mein sawal kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ko khub malum hai ke wo ( badey ho kar) kya amal kartey.
6598,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ki aulad ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah khub janta hai ke wo kya amal kartey.
6599,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi bachcha aisa nahi hai jo fitrat par na paida hota ho. lekin uske waalidain usey Yahudi ya nasrani bana detey hain jaisa ke tumharey janwaron ke bachchey paida hotey hain. kya unmein koi kaan kata paida hota hai? wo to tum hi uska kaan kaat detey ho.
6600,sahaba ne arz kya : phir ya Rasulullah ! us bachchey ke mutaalliq kya khayal hai jo bachpan hi mein mar gaya ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah khub janta hai ke wo ( bada ho kar) kya amal karta.
6601,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi aurat apni kisi ( deenii ( behan ki talaaq ka mutalba ( shauhar se) na karey ke uske ghar ko apne hi liye khas kar lena chaahey. balke usey nikah (doosri aurat ki maujoodgii mein bhi) kar lena chahiye kyonke usey utnaa hi milega jitna uske muqaddar mein hoga.
6602,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki saahibzaadiyon mein se aik ka bulaawaa aaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Sad , Ubai-bin-Kab aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they. bulaney waley ne aa kar kaha ke unka bachcha (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka nawaasaa) jaan nikalney ki haalat mein hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kelha bheja ke Allah hi ka hai jo wo leta hai, isliye wo sabr karein aur Allah se ajr ki ummeed rakhein."
6603,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they ke qabila Ansar ka aik aadmi aaya aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham laundiyon se ham-bistarii kartey hain aur maal se mohabbat kartey hain. aap ka azl ke barey mein kya khayal hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha tum aisa kartey ho, tumharey liye kuchh qabahat nahi agar tum aisa na karo, kyonke jis jaan ki bhi paidaaish Allah ne likh di hai wo zaroor paida ho kar rahegi ."
6604,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik khutba diya aur qiyamat tak koi ( deeni ( cheez aisi nahi chhodi jiska bayan na kya ho, jisey yad rakhna tha us ne yad rakha aur jisey bhoolnaa tha wo bhool gaya, jab main unki koi cheez dekhta hun jisey main bhool chuka hun to is tarah usey pehchan leta hun jis tarah wo shakhs jiski koi cheez gum ho gaee ho ke jab wo usey dekhta hai to fauran pehchan leta hai."
6605,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein aik lakdi thi jis se aap zameen kured rahe they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (usi beech mein) farmaya ke tum mein se har shakhs ka jahannam ka ya jannat ka thikana likha ja chuka hai, aik musalman ne is par arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir kyon na ham is par bharosa kar lein ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi amal karo kyonke har shakhs (apni taqdeer ke mutabiq ( amal ki aasani paata hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki) فأما من أعطى واتقى‏ ( to jisne Allah ki raah mein diya aur taqwa ikhtiyar kya. . . الخ ."
6606,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki ladai mein maujood they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ke barey mein jo aap ke sath Sharik jihad tha aur Islam ka dawedar tha farmaya ke ye jahannami hai. jab jang honey lagi to us shakhs ne bahut jam kar ladai mein hissey liya aur bahut zyada zakhmi ho gaya phir bhi wo Sabit qadam raha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi ne aa kar arz kya : ya Rasulullah! us shakhs ke barey mein aapko malum hai jiske barey mein abhi aap ne farmaya tha ke wo jahannami hai wo to Allah ke rastey mein bahut jam kar lada hai aur bahut zyada zakhmi ho gaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ab bhi yahi farmaya ke wo jahannami hai. mumkin tha ke kuchh musalman shubeh mein pad jatey lekin is arse mein us shakhs ne zakhmon ko bardasht na kartey huey apna tarkash khola aur is mein se aik teer nikal kar apne aapko zabah kar liya. phir bahut se musalman Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein daudtey huey pahunchey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala ne aap ki baat sach kar dikhai . us shakhs ne apne aapko halaak karke apni jaan khud hi khatm kar dali . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par farmaya ke aey Bilal ! utho aur logon mein elaan kar do ke jannat mein sirf momin hi dakhil hoga aur ye ke Allah Taala is Deen ki khidmat w madad be-deen aadmi se bhi karaataa hai."
6607,"aik shakhs jo musalmanon ki taraf se badi bahaadurii se lad raha tha aur us jang main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi maujood they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha aur farmaya ke jo kisi jahannami shakhs ko dekhnaa chahta hai wo us shakhs ko dekh ley chunanche wo shakhs jab isi tarah ladney mein masroof tha aur mushrekeen ko apni bahaadurii ki wjah se sakht tar takaaleef mein mubtala kar raha tha to aik musalman uske peechhey peechhey chala , aakhir wo shakhs zakhmi ho gaya aur jaldi se mar jana chaha , isliye us ne apni talwaar ki dhaar apne seeney par laga li aur talwaar uske shaanon ko paar karti hui nikal gaee. iske baad peechhaa karne wala shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein daudta hua hazir hua aur arz kya, main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke baat kya hai? un sahib ne kaha ke aap ne falan shakhs ke barey mein farmaya tha ke jo kisi jahannami ko dekhnaa chahta hai wo us shakhs ko dekh ley halanke wo shakhs musalmanon ki taraf se badi bahaadurii se lad raha tha. main samjha ke wo us haalat mein nahi marega. lekin jab wo zakhmi ho gaya to jaldi se mar janey ki khahish mein us ne khudkushii kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke banda dozkhiyon ke se kaam karta rehta hai halanke wo jannati hota hai (usi tarah doosra banda ( jannatiyon ke kaam karta rehta hai halanke wo dozakhi hota hai, bila shubah amalon ka eitibaar khaatme par hai."
6608,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nazar manney se mana kya tha aur farmaya tha ke nazar kisi cheez ko nahi lautaatii, nazar sirf kanjoos ke dil se paisaa nikaaltii hai."
6609,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nazar ( mannat ( insan ko koi cheez nahi deti jo main ( rab ( ne uski taqdeer mein na likhi ho balke wo taqdeer deti hai jo main ( rab ( ne uske liye muqarrar kar di hai, albatta iske zariey mein kanjoos ka maal nikalwaa leta hun."
6610,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang mein they aur jab bhi ham kisi bulandi par chadhtey ya kisi nashebii ilaqe mein utartey to takbeer buland awaz se kehtey. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey qareeb aaey aur farmaya ''aey logo ! apne aap par raham karo, kyonke tum kisi behrey ya ghair maujood ko nahi pukaartey balke tum us zaat ko pukaartey ho jo bahut zyada sunney wala bada dekhney wala hai.'' phir farmaya : aey Abdullah-bin-Qais ! ( abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) kya main tumhen aik kalima na sikhaa dun jo jannat ke khazaanon mein se hai. (wo kalima hai) لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله yaanii taqat w quwwat Allah ke siwa aur kisi ke paas nahi."
6611,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab bhi koi shakhs Hakim hota hai to uske salaahkaar aur musheer 2 tarah ke hotey hain aik to wo jo usey neki aur bhalai ka hukm detey hain aur is par Ubhaartey rahtey hain aur doosrey wo jo usey burai ka hukm detey hain aur is par usey Ubhaartey rahtey hain aur masoom wo hai jisey Allah mehfooz rakhey.''
6612,"ye jo ( لمم (ka lafz Quran mein aaya hai to main ( لمم (ke mushabeh (similar) is baat se zyada koi baat nahi janta jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki hai ke Allah Taala ne insan ke liye zina ka koi na koi hissey likh diya hai jis se usey laa-muhaalaa guzarna hai, to aankh ka zina ( ghair-maharam ko) dekhnaa hai, zaban ka zina ghair-maharam se guftgu karna hai, dil ka zina khahish aur shahwat hai aur sharmgah uski tasdeeq kar deti hai ya usey jhutlaa deti hai. aur Shababaa ne bayan kya ke ham se Warqaa ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Taaoos ne, unse unke walid ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir us hadis ko naql kya."
6613,"aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat ( وما جعلنا الرؤيا التي أريناك إلا فتنة للناس‏ ( ''aur wo rua'yaa jo ham ne tumhen dikhaya hai usey ham ne sirf logon ke liye aazmaish banaya hai.'' ke mutaalliq kaha ke us se murad aankh ka dekhnaa hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us meraaj ki raat dikhaya gaya tha. jab aapko baitul-maqdis tak raat ko ley jaya gaya tha, kaha ke Quran Majeed main ( الشجرة الملعونة ( se murad ( zaqqoom . Mina (ka darakht hai."
6614,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya '' Adam aur Musa ne mubaahasa kya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne Adam (Alaihissalam) se kaha : Adam ! aap hamarey bap hain magar aap hi ne hamein mahroom kya aur jannat se nikala . Adam (Alaihissalam) ne Musa (Alaihissalam) se kaha Musa aapko Allah Taala ne ham kalaamii ke liye barguzeeda kya aur apne hath se aap ke liye Taurait ko likha . kya aap mujhey aik aisey kaam par malaamat kartey hain jo Allah Taala ne mujhey paida karne se chalis (40) saal pahley meri taqdeer mein likh diya tha. aakhir Adam (Alaihissalam) bahas mein Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aaey. teen martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla farmaya, Sufiyan ne usi asnaad se bayan kya, kaha ham se abu-Zinaad ne bayan kya, unse Aaraj ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir yahi hadis naql ki."
6615,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wo dua likh kar bhejo jo tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ke baad kartey suni hai. chunanche Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh ko likhwaayaa . unhon-ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har farz Namaz ke baad ye dua kya kartey they اللهم لا مانع لما أعطيت ، Mina wla معطي لما منعت ، Mina wla ينفع ذا الجد منك الجد ''Allaah ke siwa koi maabood nahi wo aik hai iska koi Sharik nahi, aey Allah ! jo to dena chahey usey koi rokney wala nahi aur jo to roknaa chahey usey koi dene wala nahi aur terey samney daulat waley ki daulat kuchh kaam nahi de sakti aur ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke mujh ko Abda ne khabar di aur unhein Wardaa ne khabar di, phir iske baad main Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya to maine dekha ke wo logon ko is dua ke padhney ka hukm de rahe they."
6616,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah se panah maanga karo aazmaish ki mashaqqat, bad-bakhtii ki pastii, burey khaatmey aur dushman ke hansney se."
6617,aksar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qism khaya kartey they ke nahi ! dilon ko pherney waley ki qasam.
6618,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne-Sayyaad se farmaya ke maine terey liye aik baat dil mein chipa rakhi hai) bata wo kya hai? ( usne kaha ke '' dhuaan '' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bad-bakht ! apni haisiyat se aagey na badh . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : aap mujhey ijazat dein to main uski gardan mar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey chhod do, agar ye wahi ( dajjal ( hua to tum is par qaabu nahi pa saktey aur agar ye wo na hua to usey qatl karne main tumharey liye koi bhalai nahi."
6619,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se taaoon ke mutaalliq puchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye azab tha aur Allah Taala jis par chahta hai usey bhejta tha. phir Allah Taala ne usey mominon ke liye rehmat bana diya, koi bhi banda agar kisi aisey Shahar mein hai jis mein taaoon ki wabaa phootii hui hai aur is mein thehra hai aur us Shahar se bhaagaa nahi sabr kiye huey hai aur is par ajr ka ummeedwaar hai aur yaqin rakhta hai ke us tak sirf wahi cheez pahunch sakti hai jo Allah ne uski taqdeer mein likh di hai to usey Shahid ke barabar sawab milega."
6620,"maine Khandaq ki jang ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap hamarey sath mitti utha rahe they aur ye kehtey jatey they. ''Allah ki qism , agar Allah na hota to ham hidayat na pa saktey. na roza rakh saktey aur na Namaz padh saktey. to aey Allah ! ham par sakeenat nazil farma aur jab saamnaa ho to hamein Sabit qadam rakh aur mushrekeen ne ham par zyadti ki hai. jab wo kisi fitne ka irada kartey hain to ham inkar kartey hain.''"
